om%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090616%2F12882622&h=41d91fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090616/12882622</a><br />\n希望咁多年有改善啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街 隻Perrier礦泉水成日飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前返工日日飲佢半打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc19a1070543cca5debdd347f135c74cf599c476","tid":446592,"uid":105738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"好撚難飲，成陣臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：只飲evian"},{"pid":"0dad822036b606c9acfbe35026296a87d25f1f94","tid":446592,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T17:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090616/12882622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090616%2F12882622&d=xoqa1vq5fhZbZ0xtEAaRBNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7c86008f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090616%2F12882622&h=41d91fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090616/12882622</a><br />\n希望咁多年有改善啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街 隻Perrier礦泉水成日飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前返工日日飲佢半打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街   我都好中意飲  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9308f2fc4fa31a064bae5a5d2d7b100383505c","tid":446592,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T18:24:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090616/12882622\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090616%2F12882622&d=xoqa1vq5fhZbZ0xtEAaRBNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7c86008f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20090616%2F12882622&h=41d91fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20090616/12882622</a><br />\n希望咁多年有改善啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街 隻Perrier礦泉水成日飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前返工日日飲佢半打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街   我都好中意飲  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以一個60公斤重的成人計算，每日亞硝酸鹽攝取上限為4.2毫克，要每日飲10升 Perrier才會超標。如攝取過量亞硝酸鹽，會導致血氧過少，及出現頭痛、呼吸困難等症狀。<br />\nPerrier代理商反駁消委會指，在法國測試顯示每升礦泉水亞硝酸鹽含量是0.05毫克，符合歐盟標準，質疑消委會測試是否準確。<br />\n<br />\n當你消委真係準,都要每日飲10公升先會超標,驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6c103e1e749aaa3d51e19d89fff4320168e5de","tid":446592,"uid":71303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T21:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果啲fuck boy亂咁襯對yeezy <br />\n我就偏向清純好似fiji <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cbb784db43